From Michael Siemon Subject Re Homosexuality issues in Christianity In article M gchin writes Let me say that the life death and resurrection of Jesus Christ is central to If you personally believe that Jesus Christ died for you you are a part of the Christian body of We are all still We don't know it all but homosexual or heterosexual we all strive to follow The world is dying and needs to hear about Jesus Are you working together with other Christians to spread the Gospel Let me salute Gary Chin for speaking the gospel which is our source of Any who will follow his example and accept the priorities Christ commands of us that the weightier matters of the law are justice and mercy and good faith is my brother or sister in Christ and I will attend to such a person with humility and We may not in the end agree siblings often don't but we can at least Michael Siemon I say You are gods sons of the Most High all of you nevertheless or you shall die like men and fall like any Psalm